summary: Many people remember Toby Macquire in the spider man 3 movie as overacting the “cool boy” scenes and rendering that film as...
body: Many people remember Toby Macquire in the spider man 3 movie as overacting the “cool boy” scenes and rendering that film as camp. This is not entirely incorrect, but overlooks clear subtext. Spider man is at his lowest point when his Masculine physique and confidence is at his highest. This movie casually and clearly states that any masculinity centering around physique and the sexual dominance of women is inherently off putting. This flies in the face of the 80s hypermasculinity that preceded it and is faithful to Spider-Man’s character. In this essay I will…..
